cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.NA, cs.CC

The paper deals with stability analysis of linear dynamical systems, which is a topic in control theory and systems engineering. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves linear algebraic tools and numerical examples, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). The paper's focus on matrices and their properties suggests that it could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
